Purchasing Platform, LLC

Savings and Efficiency for the Real Estate Industry






Stage

Full Product Ready



Industry

Real Estate



Location

Chicago, IL, USA



Currency

USD



Founded

January 2012



Employees

8



Website

purchasingplatform.com

















Company Summary





Purchasing Platform is a membership-based online marketplace helping real estate operators save time and money. We provide a consolidated purchasing solution with end column pricing from top vendors. The result is significant discounts on everything from office supplies to maintenance equipment in a client-controlled spending environment.






















Team













Peter Hepner

Chief Executive Officer




Peter is a twenty-year real estate veteran. Prior to founding Purchasing Platform, he spent nearly ten years leading asset management at a $3 billion real estate investment company. He is a graduate of DePauw University in Greencastle, IN, and is active in a number of board and advisory roles including Holy Trinity High School and The Alison Tobey Smart Memorial Fund.















Advisors













Michael Gray; Neal Gerber & Eisenberg, LLP

